org.hps.record.triggerbank

Enum TriggerType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<TriggerType>
      • org.hps.record.triggerbank.TriggerType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<TriggerType>

    public enum TriggerType
extends Enum<TriggerType>
    Provides bit mask checks for the trigger types defined in EVIO Event types.
